Introduction of Armenia

Armenia is a country in Southwestern Asia.The neighborhood countries of the Armenia are,Georgia,Azerbaijan,Iran,Nakhijevan and Turkey.Territory is about 29.74 thousand square kilometers. As of 2022 January 1,population of the country is 2961 thousand.

Climate

Armenia has significant annual variance in temperature.There are four seasons Winter that lasting from June to mid September,Summer, short Spring and long Autumn.in summer temperature is fluctuates between 22 and 36 Celsius.

Economy

The economy of the Armenia relies heavily on investment and support from Armenians abroad.

Health

In Armenia medical treatment in hospitals and clinics is free of charge for all citizens.

Discussion

According to the analysis of Armenia COVID 19 cases data set,we cant say that Armenia is extremely god or bad.They managed the deaths with respect to the confirmed cases.But after the first six months 2021 ,recovery cases are reduced.There fore Armenia should pay attention for recovering the COVID cases.Their number of confirmed cases are as twice as recoveries.Therefore make their attention to reduce corona cases by make COVID rules and health care followings,will be a decision. Analyzing their neighborhood countries Iran & Turkey provide surprising result of death cases.While others are surrounded countries,I choose Sri Lanka also compared as it is also a Asian country and as Sri Lankans our responsibility is save from COVID 19 by following health care rules.

Conclusions

In 2021-2022 Armenia has approximately 246 average daily corona cases. Daily 249 cases are recognize as COVID.Approximately 9 people are died daily from COVID 19. From the middle of the year 2020 to middle of the 2021 covid cases are managed somewhat good. As overall Armenia controls the corona in their country somewhat good. Among the neighboring countries Armenia also in same level from covid controlling.
